Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.11,0:06:19.98,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1600,200)\fad(1000,0)}第一只
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.11,0:06:19.98,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1600,320)\fad(1000,0)\fs120}鹤立鸡群
Dialogue: 5,0:00:08.22,0:00:10.87,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ねえねえ　ママ　今日のご飯何？
Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.87,0:00:12.82,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,そうね…
Dialogue: 5,0:00:14.30,0:00:17.66,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,今日はパパいないから　鳥繁さんで焼き鳥買っちゃおっか
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.66,0:00:20.12,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,えっ　やったー
Dialogue: 5,0:00:20.12,0:00:24.80,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,じゃあ僕　砂肝とこめかみとさえずりとおたふくとぼんじり
Dialogue: 5,0:00:26.21,0:00:28.73,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,あんた本当に渋いわね
Dialogue: 5,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.19,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,パパの影響かな…
Dialogue: 5,0:00:30.19,0:00:32.65,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,あ　あと鳥もつ煮　ね
Dialogue: 5,0:00:32.65,0:00:34.62,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,どこのおじさんよ
Dialogue: 5,0:00:55.82,0:00:56.69,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,なんだ？
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.69,0:00:57.63,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,鬼獣？
Dialogue: 5,0:00:58.06,0:00:59.23,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,鬼獣に…
Dialogue: 5,0:01:08.88,0:01:14.15,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,坊や…私の…坊や…
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.24,0:01:18.65,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,どこ…どこにいるの？
Dialogue: 5,0:01:18.22,0:01:19.42,Text - JP - UP,,0,0,0,,助けて
Dialogue: 5,0:01:30.10,0:01:32.54,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,私の坊や…
Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.84,0:01:40.83,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ママ
Dialogue: 5,0:01:40.83,0:01:41.99,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ユウキ
Dialogue: 5,0:01:44.46,0:01:46.21,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,見つけた
Dialogue: 5,0:01:49.57,0:01:50.55,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ママ
Dialogue: 5,0:01:50.55,0:01:52.55,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ユウキ！
Dialogue: 5,0:01:53.37,0:01:54.80,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ママ！
Dialogue: 5,0:01:55.60,0:01:58.53,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,私の…坊や…
Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.24,0:02:04.23,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,私の…もの…
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.94,0:02:08.07,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ユウキ！
Dialogue: 5,0:02:21.67,0:02:23.81,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ユウキ！
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.16,0:02:41.93,Text - JP,,0,800,0,,返して…私の坊や…
Dialogue: 5,0:02:40.74,0:02:45.23,Text - JP,,800,0,0,,これ以上　てめえらの好きにはさせねえ
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.23,0:02:51.69,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,坊や…どこ…坊や…どこ
Dialogue: 5,0:02:52.29,0:02:55.26,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,どこにいるの　坊や
Dialogue: 5,0:02:55.26,0:02:59.74,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,てめえら全員　ぶっ倒す
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.74,0:03:22.37,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,これは　一羽の鶏が　人類を救う物語である
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.62,0:05:56.72,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,待って…
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.55,0:06:00.34,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,行ってしまうの？
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.21,0:06:05.35,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,俺はさすらいの渡り鳥　安らぎは似合わねえ
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.16,0:06:07.72,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,遊びだったのね
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.88,0:06:09.85,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.34,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ただの盛りだ
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.29,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,群鶏一鶴
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.61,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,うまい
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.03,0:06:45.96,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,この香ばしい香りと程よい苦味
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.81,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,やはり朝食はカメムシに限る
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.21,0:06:54.88,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,しかも　これを食べると　胃腸の調子が整い　快便になる
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.58,0:07:02.61,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,美味くて健康に良い　まさに一石二鳥の食い物だぜ
Dialogue: 5,0:07:15.29,0:07:18.19,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,あー　鶏
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.47,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,トサカ可愛い
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.47,0:07:23.08,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,野良鶏かな　どっから来たの
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.24,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,動物園じゃん？
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.77,Text - JP,,600,0,0,,ウケる
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.98,Text - JP,,0,600,0,,子供は嫌いだ
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.97,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,無神経でわがままでギャーギャーうるさい
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.19,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ねぇきみ　これ食べる？
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.66,0:07:36.94,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,フライドチキン　おいしいよ
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.35,0:07:40.01,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,こいつ　正気か？
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.24,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,面白えもん見つけたぜ
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.24,0:07:47.65,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,そんなことしたら可哀想でしょ
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.49,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,うるせえクソガキ
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.64,0:07:51.55,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,行こうぜ
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.55,0:07:52.54,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,えん
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.61,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,おお　すげえ　トサカ
Dialogue: 5,0:07:54.61,0:07:56.31,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,自分だってガキじゃん
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.31,0:07:57.75,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,そうだそうだ
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.52,0:08:00.88,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,こいつどうする？
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.88,0:08:02.41,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,俺　食ってみてぇ
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.41,0:08:05.04,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,バカ　変な病気持ってたらどうすんだよ
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.04,0:08:05.76,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.76,0:08:08.88,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,それよりか　うちの猫の餌にするってのはどう
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.26,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,はっ　それいいね
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.02,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,待って
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.46,0:08:16.14,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,まてこら
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.41,0:08:20.27,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,付き合ってられるか　クソガキが
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.65,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,止まれ　この野郎
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.74,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ちっ　しつっこいぜ
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.31,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,待ちやがれ
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.44,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,どうしたんだい？
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.44,0:08:54.56,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,その鶏　俺たちのなんだ
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.26,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,はあ
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.56,0:09:02.19,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,それはおかしいのう
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.58,0:09:05.08,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,この鶏はうちで飼っておるんだが
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.02,0:09:07.57,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ほら　コケ助
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.49,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,あれほど庭からは出ないよう言ったろ
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.49,0:09:12.07,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,コ…コケ助？
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.49,0:09:15.20,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,すまないね　今度から気をつけるよ
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.29,0:09:20.46,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ちっ　行こうぜ
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.99,0:09:27.21,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,助かったぜ　じいさん
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.97,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,あの鶏　本当にあのじいさんのかな
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.97,0:09:38.22,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,バカ　嘘に決まってんだろ　クソジジイが
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.53,0:09:39.73,Text - JP - UP,,0,0,0,,ノルマ…ノルマ…ノルマ…
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.22,0:09:41.14,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,あのおじいさん　１人で食うつもりかな
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.58,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,１人で食わないよ
Dialogue: 5,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.85,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,独り占めだな
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.80,0:09:46.98,Text - JP - UP,,0,0,0,,今月こそ…絶対…絶対達成する…ノルマ…
Dialogue: 5,0:09:48.32,0:09:50.07,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,世話になったなじいさん
Dialogue: 5,0:09:50.47,0:09:53.25,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,俺にはやらなきゃならねえことがあるんでな
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.87,0:09:58.93,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,すまないね　こんなものしかないんだが
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.00,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,玄米にコーンに大葉の葉？
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.35,0:10:04.41,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,じいさん…
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.62,0:10:09.09,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,これは紛れもなくスペシャルなご馳走だぜ！
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.37,0:10:13.47,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,美味しいか　よかったよかった
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.26,0:10:25.73,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ばあさんも　うちに遊びに来るスズメによく餌をやっとった
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.40,0:10:29.89,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,今思えば…
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.79,0:10:32.98,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,教師などさっさと引退して
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.83,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ばあさんとの時間をもっと作ってやればよかった
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.63,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ほら　喧嘩しないで
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.63,0:10:48.99,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ゆっくりお食べ
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.14,0:11:03.69,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,つまらん話をしてしまった
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.22,0:11:08.02,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,でも　なぜだかお前さんには　何でも話したくなる
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.11,0:11:11.00,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,分かるぜ　じいさん
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.82,0:11:15.05,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,俺もあいつとの時間をもっと作っておけば…
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.64,0:11:16.91,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.79,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.60,0:11:25.78,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.54,0:11:29.67,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃーん！
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.92,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,サ…サラ…
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.07,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃん！
Dialogue: 5,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.80,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,サラ！
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.69,0:11:48.83,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃーん！
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.94,0:11:53.19,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,サラ！
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.91,0:12:09.27,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,な…なんじゃ？
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.23,0:12:19.55,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,モデルアップグレード
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.55,0:12:22.35,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,高額トレードイン
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.76,0:12:27.61,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,鬼獣出没注意報が　発令されました
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.36,0:12:34.24,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,速やかに　安全な場所に　避難してください
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.57,0:12:39.82,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,鬼獣
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.33,0:12:46.83,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,今月こそは　ノルマをこなす
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.29,0:12:53.78,Text - JP,,0,600,0,,助けて
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.94,0:12:54.23,Text - JP,,600,0,0,,助けて
Dialogue: 5,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.21,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,さっきのガキ
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.33,Text - JP - UP,,0,0,0,,ヒロシ！
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.22,0:13:01.35,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,い…いたぇ…
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.90,0:13:03.22,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,いたぁ…
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.77,0:13:11.15,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ノ…ル…マ…
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.05,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,早く逃げろ！
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.37,Text - JP - UP,,0,0,0,,達成…
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.24,0:13:21.24,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,じいさん！
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.20,0:13:39.63,Text - JP,,800,0,0,,リコール？
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.02,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,今のうちじゃん　さあ
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.44,0:13:59.59,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,てめえ　年寄り子供に何してくれてんだ
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.10,0:14:03.45,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,超絶　トサカにくるぜ！
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.84,0:14:33.19,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ノルマ達成
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.70,0:14:42.15,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,てめえを　ぶっ倒す！
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.78,0:14:47.33,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,特別仕様車
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.16,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ハイブリッド車
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.25,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,水素エンジン
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.18,0:15:14.19,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,目指せ　全国　一！
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.06,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,国産車
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.84,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,外国車
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.05,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,国産車
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.76,0:15:44.97,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,すげえ
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.73,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,とどめだ
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.54,0:16:14.75,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,食らえ
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.44,0:16:17.83,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,鴣！
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.29,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,鴃！
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.84,0:16:20.67,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,鶻！
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.42,0:16:23.71,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,鵁！
Dialogue: 5,0:16:49.00,0:16:52.17,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,売上…月報…
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.18,0:17:15.51,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,な…なんだ今の…
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.51,0:17:16.88,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,これはもしや…
Dialogue: 5,0:17:17.64,0:17:20.40,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,共振と言われる現象かもしれん
Dialogue: 5,0:17:20.40,0:17:21.87,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,共…共振？
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.87,0:17:25.23,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,君たちも　テレビや映画で見たことないかね　
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.19,0:17:28.83,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,声だけでグラスを割る映像を
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.62,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,共振とは確か…
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.90,0:17:41.37,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,声の周波数と　物体の周波数が一致した時に　起きる現象だったはずだが
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.52,0:17:47.83,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,こんな巨大生物を破裂させるほどの　破壊力があるものなのか
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.22,0:17:54.94,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,あ…あの鶏は…
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.73,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,一体…
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.08,0:19:03.31,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,痣がない
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.73,0:19:05.72,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,やはりこいつじゃなかったか
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.91,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,こりゃひでえな
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.67,0:19:13.30,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,じいさんの庭　汚れちゃったね
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.18,0:19:21.15,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,もしかして　掃除をしようと言うのかい？
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.45,0:19:27.93,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,誰か　怪我をされた方？
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.25,0:19:30.21,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,そこ気を付けて　ガラスの破片があるから
Dialogue: 5,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.94,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,怪我人通ります
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.53,0:19:37.47,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,まだゴミ袋はありますか？
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.47,0:19:40.16,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,はいはい　まだまだありますよ
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.29,0:19:45.16,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,よいっしょう
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.57,0:19:48.38,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ふっ　終わった
Dialogue: 5,0:19:49.13,0:19:52.65,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,へんけどよ　怪獣やっつけわ掃除はするわ
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.65,0:19:55.03,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,お前　めちゃくちゃな鶏だな
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.24,0:19:58.13,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,あれ　あいつは？
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.30,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,あれ？
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.51,0:20:03.47,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,コケ助…
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.79,0:20:13.37,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,俺の名はコケ助　ではなく　ケイジ
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.90,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,さすらいの渡り鳥だ
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.75,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,この町ともおさらばだぜ
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.26,0:20:22.83,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,じいさん　ごちそうの借りは返したぜ
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.24,0:20:25.18,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,鬼獣をぶっ倒してな
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.76,0:20:26.83,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,それと…
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.90,0:20:30.71,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,庭の掃除もきっちりしたぜ
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.72,0:20:37.70,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,立つ鳥跡を濁さず　それが　俺のプライドなんでな
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.68,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,さてと…
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.31,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,行ってしまうの？
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.80,0:20:49.74,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,女を泣かせたまま去るのは　俺の主義じゃねえ
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.08,0:20:52.82,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,待たせたな　戻ってきたぜ
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.32,0:21:10.44,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,次の町が　俺を待ってるぜ
Dialogue: 5,0:22:51.03,0:22:52.85,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,見て
Dialogue: 5,0:22:53.28,0:22:56.61,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　見てよ
Dialogue: 5,0:22:57.90,0:22:59.52,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,気持ち悪い
Dialogue: 5,0:22:59.52,0:23:00.61,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,変態よ
Dialogue: 5,0:23:00.61,0:23:04.61,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,視線　１人占め
Dialogue: 5,0:23:06.74,0:23:10.33,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,汚い体を　見せるんじゃないわよ
Dialogue: 5,0:23:16.07,0:23:18.71,Text - JP,,1400,0,0,,サンダーバード！
Dialogue: 5,0:23:27.14,0:23:28.91,Text - JP,,0,0,0,,気持ち悪いわね
Dialogue: 6,0:00:08.22,0:00:10.87,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,妈妈  妈妈  今天晚上吃什么？
Dialogue: 6,0:00:10.87,0:00:12.82,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我想想啊…
Dialogue: 6,0:00:14.30,0:00:17.66,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,今天爸爸不在家  我们去烧鸟店吃烤鸡串吧
Dialogue: 6,0:00:17.66,0:00:20.12,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 6,0:00:20.12,0:00:24.80,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,那我要鸡胗  猪头肉  鸡食管  鸡胸腺还有鸡屁股
Dialogue: 6,0:00:26.21,0:00:28.73,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,你的口味真重啊
Dialogue: 6,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.19,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,是受爸爸影响吗…
Dialogue: 6,0:00:30.19,0:00:32.65,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我还要日式炖鸡杂  行不行
Dialogue: 6,0:00:32.65,0:00:34.62,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,你这是什么大叔口味啊
Dialogue: 6,0:00:55.82,0:00:56.69,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 6,0:00:56.69,0:00:57.63,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,是鬼兽？
Dialogue: 6,0:00:58.06,0:00:59.23,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,鬼兽来了…
Dialogue: 6,0:01:08.88,0:01:14.15,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,孩子…我的…孩子…
Dialogue: 6,0:01:15.24,0:01:18.65,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,在哪…你在哪儿？
Dialogue: 6,0:01:18.22,0:01:19.42,Text - CN - UP,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 6,0:01:30.10,0:01:32.54,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我的孩子…
Dialogue: 6,0:01:39.84,0:01:40.83,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 6,0:01:40.83,0:01:41.99,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,由纪
Dialogue: 6,0:01:44.46,0:01:46.21,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 6,0:01:49.57,0:01:50.55,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 6,0:01:50.55,0:01:52.55,Text - CN,,20,0,0,,由纪！
Dialogue: 6,0:01:53.37,0:01:54.80,Text - CN,,20,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 6,0:01:55.60,0:01:58.53,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我的…孩子…
Dialogue: 6,0:02:00.24,0:02:04.23,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,你是…我的…
Dialogue: 6,0:02:05.94,0:02:08.07,Text - CN,,20,0,0,,由纪！
Dialogue: 6,0:02:21.67,0:02:23.81,Text - CN,,20,0,0,,由纪！
Dialogue: 6,0:02:38.16,0:02:41.93,Text - CN,,0,800,0,,把我的孩子…还给我…
Dialogue: 6,0:02:40.74,0:02:45.23,Text - CN,,800,0,0,,我不会再任由你肆意妄为
Dialogue: 6,0:02:45.23,0:02:51.69,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,孩子…你在哪…孩子…你在哪
Dialogue: 6,0:02:52.29,0:02:55.26,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿  我的孩子
Dialogue: 6,0:02:55.26,0:02:59.74,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我会打倒所有鬼兽
Dialogue: 6,0:03:12.74,0:03:22.37,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,这是一只鸡拯救人类的故事
Dialogue: 6,0:05:55.62,0:05:56.72,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 6,0:05:58.55,0:06:00.34,Text - CN,,10,0,0,,你要走了吗？
Dialogue: 6,0:06:01.21,0:06:05.35,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我乃漂泊的候鸟  安定的生活不适合我
Dialogue: 6,0:06:06.16,0:06:07.72,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,你在玩弄我的感情吗
Dialogue: 6,0:06:08.88,0:06:09.85,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,非也
Dialogue: 6,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.34,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我只是发情了
Dialogue: 6,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.29,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,鹤立鸡群
Dialogue: 6,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.61,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,美味
Dialogue: 6,0:06:43.03,0:06:45.96,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,芬芳馥郁  苦味恰到好处
Dialogue: 6,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.81,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,早饭就得吃臭屁虫
Dialogue: 6,0:06:49.21,0:06:54.88,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,而且吃它还能调理肠胃  有助排便
Dialogue: 6,0:06:57.58,0:07:02.61,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,既好吃又健康  真是一石二鸟的美食
Dialogue: 6,0:07:15.29,0:07:18.19,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,看  有只鸡
Dialogue: 6,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.47,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,鸡冠好可爱
Dialogue: 6,0:07:20.47,0:07:23.08,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,你是野生的鸡吗  从哪儿来的呀
Dialogue: 6,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.24,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,动物园出逃的吧？
Dialogue: 6,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.77,Text - CN,,600,0,0,,笑死啦
Dialogue: 6,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.98,Text - CN,,0,600,0,,我讨厌小孩子
Dialogue: 6,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.97,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,不顾他人感受  任性妄为  还吵死人
Dialogue: 6,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.19,Text - CN,,10,0,0,,喂  你要吃这个吗？
Dialogue: 6,0:07:33.66,0:07:36.94,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,这是炸鸡  超好吃的
Dialogue: 6,0:07:37.35,0:07:40.01,Text - CN,,10,0,0,,这瓜娃子认真的？
Dialogue: 6,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.24,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,抓到个好玩的东西
Dialogue: 6,0:07:45.24,0:07:47.65,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,你们这样对它  它很可怜啊
Dialogue: 6,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.49,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,别嚷嚷  臭小鬼
Dialogue: 6,0:07:50.64,0:07:51.55,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 6,0:07:51.55,0:07:52.54,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 6,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.61,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,这鸡的鸡冠真大啊
Dialogue: 6,0:07:54.61,0:07:56.31,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,你们不也是小鬼嘛
Dialogue: 6,0:07:56.31,0:07:57.75,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 6,0:07:59.52,0:08:00.88,Text - CN,,10,0,0,,怎么处置它？
Dialogue: 6,0:08:00.88,0:08:02.41,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我想烧了吃了
Dialogue: 6,0:08:02.41,0:08:05.04,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,蠢货  要是它有鸡瘟之类的病怎么办
Dialogue: 6,0:08:05.04,0:08:05.76,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,也是哦
Dialogue: 6,0:08:05.76,0:08:08.88,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,话说不如拿它来喂我家猫  怎么样
Dialogue: 6,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.26,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,这点子不错
Dialogue: 6,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.02,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 6,0:08:14.46,0:08:16.14,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 6,0:08:17.41,0:08:20.27,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我没闲工夫陪你们闹  臭小鬼
Dialogue: 6,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.65,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,臭鸡给我站住
Dialogue: 6,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.74,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,啧  真是难缠
Dialogue: 6,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.31,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 6,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.44,Text - CN,,10,0,0,,这是怎么啦？
Dialogue: 6,0:08:52.44,0:08:54.56,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,这只鸡是我们的
Dialogue: 6,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.26,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 6,0:09:00.56,0:09:02.19,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,那真是奇怪了
Dialogue: 6,0:09:02.58,0:09:05.08,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,这鸡一直是我家在养的
Dialogue: 6,0:09:06.02,0:09:07.57,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,喂  咯哒助
Dialogue: 6,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.49,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,都跟你说那么多遍别到处乱跑
Dialogue: 6,0:09:10.49,0:09:12.07,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,咯…咯哒助？
Dialogue: 6,0:09:12.49,0:09:15.20,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊  我以后会看好我家鸡
Dialogue: 6,0:09:18.29,0:09:20.46,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,嘁  走吧
Dialogue: 6,0:09:24.99,0:09:27.21,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,真是帮大忙了  老爷子
Dialogue: 6,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.97,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,那只鸡真的是老爷爷养的吗
Dialogue: 6,0:09:34.97,0:09:38.22,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,蠢货  那个老登肯定在扯谎
Dialogue: 6,0:09:35.53,0:09:39.73,Text - CN - UP,,0,0,0,,指标…指标…指标…
Dialogue: 6,0:09:38.22,0:09:41.14,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,那个老爷爷是想独吞一整只鸡吧
Dialogue: 6,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.58,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,一个人吃不下那么大的鸡
Dialogue: 6,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.85,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,他要吃独食
Dialogue: 6,0:09:40.80,0:09:46.98,Text - CN - UP,,0,0,0,,这个月…我一定…一定会完成…指标…
Dialogue: 6,0:09:48.32,0:09:50.07,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,承蒙照顾了老爷子
Dialogue: 6,0:09:50.47,0:09:53.25,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我还有要事在身
Dialogue: 6,0:09:55.87,0:09:58.93,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,抱歉啦  我只有这些这些能招待你
Dialogue: 6,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.00,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,糙米  玉米还有紫苏叶？
Dialogue: 6,0:10:03.35,0:10:04.41,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,老爷子…
Dialogue: 6,0:10:05.62,0:10:09.09,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,毋庸置疑  这就是一顿丰盛的大餐！
Dialogue: 6,0:10:10.37,0:10:13.47,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,好吃吗  你喜欢吃就好
Dialogue: 6,0:10:21.26,0:10:25.73,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我家老婆子也经常喂院子里玩耍的麻雀
Dialogue: 6,0:10:28.40,0:10:29.89,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,如今回忆往昔…
Dialogue: 6,0:10:30.79,0:10:32.98,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,若是我早点退休
Dialogue: 6,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.83,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,多腾出点时间  陪陪老婆子就好了
Dialogue: 6,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.63,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,乖啦  别吵架
Dialogue: 6,0:10:46.63,0:10:48.99,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,慢慢吃吧
Dialogue: 6,0:11:01.14,0:11:03.69,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,说的都是些无聊的往事
Dialogue: 6,0:11:04.22,0:11:08.02,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,不过不知为何  面对你时我愿意倾吐任何事
Dialogue: 6,0:11:09.11,0:11:11.00,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我懂你  老爷子
Dialogue: 6,0:11:11.82,0:11:15.05,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我若是能多陪陪她就好了…
Dialogue: 6,0:11:15.64,0:11:16.91,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 6,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.79,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 6,0:11:24.60,0:11:25.78,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 6,0:11:26.54,0:11:29.67,Text - CN,,20,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 6,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.92,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,莎…莎拉…
Dialogue: 6,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.07,Text - CN,,20,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 6,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.80,Text - CN,,20,0,0,,莎拉！
Dialogue: 6,0:11:45.69,0:11:48.83,Text - CN,,20,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 6,0:11:49.94,0:11:53.19,Text - CN,,20,0,0,,莎拉！
Dialogue: 6,0:12:07.91,0:12:09.27,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,发…发生什么了？
Dialogue: 6,0:12:17.23,0:12:19.55,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,模型升级
Dialogue: 6,0:12:19.55,0:12:22.35,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,高价换购
Dialogue: 6,0:12:22.76,0:12:27.61,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,正在发布鬼兽出没警报
Dialogue: 6,0:12:28.36,0:12:34.24,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,请迅速撤离至安全区域
Dialogue: 6,0:12:38.57,0:12:39.82,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,鬼兽
Dialogue: 6,0:12:40.33,0:12:46.83,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,这个月  我一定要完成指标
Dialogue: 6,0:12:52.29,0:12:53.78,Text - CN,,0,600,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 6,0:12:52.94,0:12:54.23,Text - CN,,600,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 6,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.21,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,是刚才的小鬼
Dialogue: 6,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.33,Text - CN - UP,,20,0,0,,广志！
Dialogue: 6,0:12:59.22,0:13:01.35,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,痛…好痛…
Dialogue: 6,0:13:01.90,0:13:03.22,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,好痛啊…
Dialogue: 6,0:13:06.77,0:13:11.15,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,指…标…
Dialogue: 6,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.05,Text - CN,,20,0,0,,快跑！
Dialogue: 6,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.37,Text - CN - UP,,0,0,0,,完成…
Dialogue: 6,0:13:20.24,0:13:21.24,Text - CN,,20,0,0,,老爷子！
Dialogue: 6,0:13:38.20,0:13:39.63,Text - CN,,810,0,0,,撤销订单？
Dialogue: 6,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.02,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,就趁现在  快跑
Dialogue: 6,0:13:54.44,0:13:59.59,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,你竟敢对老人和小孩动手
Dialogue: 6,0:14:00.10,0:14:03.45,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,真是让我极度怒发冲冠！
Dialogue: 6,0:14:28.84,0:14:33.19,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,完成指标
Dialogue: 6,0:14:38.70,0:14:42.15,Text - CN,,20,0,0,,我要打败你！
Dialogue: 6,0:14:43.78,0:14:47.33,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,限定款轿车
Dialogue: 6,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.16,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,混合动力汽车
Dialogue: 6,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.25,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,氢燃料发动机
Dialogue: 6,0:15:10.18,0:15:14.19,Text - CN,,20,0,0,,目标成为全国第一！
Dialogue: 6,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.06,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,国产车
Dialogue: 6,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.84,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,进口车
Dialogue: 6,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.05,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,国产车
Dialogue: 6,0:15:43.76,0:15:44.97,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 6,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.73,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,该送你上路了
Dialogue: 6,0:16:13.54,0:16:14.75,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,吃我这招
Dialogue: 6,0:16:16.44,0:16:17.83,Text - CN,,15,0,0,,鸪！
Dialogue: 6,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.29,Text - CN,,15,0,0,,鴃！
Dialogue: 6,0:16:19.84,0:16:20.67,Text - CN,,15,0,0,,鹘！
Dialogue: 6,0:16:22.42,0:16:23.71,Text - CN,,15,0,0,,䴔！
Dialogue: 6,0:16:49.00,0:16:52.17,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,销售…月报…
Dialogue: 6,0:17:14.18,0:17:15.51,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,这…这招是什么…
Dialogue: 6,0:17:15.51,0:17:16.88,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,莫非这就是…
Dialogue: 6,0:17:17.64,0:17:20.40,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,被称之为共振的一种现象
Dialogue: 6,0:17:20.40,0:17:21.87,Text - CN,,10,0,0,,共…共振？
Dialogue: 6,0:17:21.87,0:17:25.23,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,你们应该在电视或电影里看到过
Dialogue: 6,0:17:26.19,0:17:28.83,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,只凭借声音就能打碎玻璃的画面
Dialogue: 6,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.62,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我记得共振本应是…
Dialogue: 6,0:17:34.90,0:17:41.37,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,在声音频率与物体固有频率相同时发生的现象
Dialogue: 6,0:17:42.52,0:17:47.83,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,没想到声音共振竟然能让如此巨大的生物爆炸
Dialogue: 6,0:17:52.22,0:17:54.94,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,那…那只鸡…
Dialogue: 6,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.73,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,究竟是…
Dialogue: 6,0:19:02.08,0:19:03.31,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,没有痔
Dialogue: 6,0:19:03.73,0:19:05.72,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,果然不是他
Dialogue: 6,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.91,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,真惨烈啊
Dialogue: 6,0:19:10.67,0:19:13.30,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,老爷子的庭院弄得一团糟啊
Dialogue: 6,0:19:18.18,0:19:21.15,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,你是想帮我打扫庭院吗？
Dialogue: 6,0:19:25.45,0:19:27.93,Text - CN,,10,0,0,,有人受伤了吗？
Dialogue: 6,0:19:28.25,0:19:30.21,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,那边小心点  地上都是玻璃碎片
Dialogue: 6,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.94,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,有伤员  借过一下
Dialogue: 6,0:19:35.53,0:19:37.47,Text - CN,,10,0,0,,还有垃圾袋吗？
Dialogue: 6,0:19:37.47,0:19:40.16,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,有的有的  还有很多哦
Dialogue: 6,0:19:43.29,0:19:45.16,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我丢
Dialogue: 6,0:19:45.57,0:19:48.38,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,终于打扫完了
Dialogue: 6,0:19:49.13,0:19:52.65,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,不过你不仅打倒了怪兽  还打扫了庭院
Dialogue: 6,0:19:52.65,0:19:55.03,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,你真是一只好鸡啊
Dialogue: 6,0:19:56.24,0:19:58.13,Text - CN,,10,0,0,,奇怪  那只鸡呢？
Dialogue: 6,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.30,Text - CN,,10,0,0,,哪儿去了？
Dialogue: 6,0:20:02.51,0:20:03.47,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,咯哒助…
Dialogue: 6,0:20:08.79,0:20:13.37,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我的名字不是咯哒助  而是鸡志
Dialogue: 6,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.90,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,我是只漂泊的候鸟
Dialogue: 6,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.75,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,是时候和这座小镇告别了
Dialogue: 6,0:20:19.26,0:20:22.83,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,老头子  你款待我的人情我还清了
Dialogue: 6,0:20:23.24,0:20:25.18,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,毕竟我打倒了鬼兽
Dialogue: 6,0:20:25.76,0:20:26.83,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 6,0:20:27.90,0:20:30.71,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,院子也打扫得干干净净
Dialogue: 6,0:20:31.72,0:20:37.70,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,雁过无痕叶落无声  这便是我的骄傲
Dialogue: 6,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.68,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: 6,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.31,Text - CN,,10,0,0,,你要走了吗？
Dialogue: 6,0:20:45.80,0:20:49.74,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,把女人弄哭后一走了之  可不是我的作风
Dialogue: 6,0:20:50.08,0:20:52.82,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,让你久等了  我回来了
Dialogue: 6,0:21:07.32,0:21:10.44,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,下一个小镇还在等着我
Dialogue: 6,0:22:51.03,0:22:52.85,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 6,0:22:53.28,0:22:56.61,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,你们快看我啊
Dialogue: 6,0:22:57.90,0:22:59.52,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,好恶心
Dialogue: 6,0:22:59.52,0:23:00.61,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,是变态啊
Dialogue: 6,0:23:00.61,0:23:04.61,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,你们的眼里只有我
Dialogue: 6,0:23:06.74,0:23:10.33,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,别展示你那肮脏的身体啊
Dialogue: 6,0:23:16.07,0:23:18.71,Text - CN,,1420,0,0,,雷鸟！
Dialogue: 6,0:23:27.14,0:23:28.91,Text - CN,,0,0,0,,真恶心
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.56,0:20:07.81,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.2\c&H1A1A32&\3c&H090818&\frz2.5\frx1\fry-3\pos(1302,374)}限高2.4m
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:44.53,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur4}I've been walking all alone, for a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:48.39,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur4}We fell in spite of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:51.29,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur4}I never knew what was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:58.51,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur4}Searching for the answers but where I'm s'posed to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:04.80,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur4}Til the age of so much I have lost.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.16,0:10:44.53,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur4}我踽踽独行  走过长路漫漫
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.48,0:10:48.39,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur4}我们曾竭力抗争却一败涂地
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.39,0:10:51.29,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur4}我不曾知晓何为正道
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.83,0:10:58.51,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur4}终其一生寻找答案  可我又该何去何从？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.34,0:11:04.80,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur4}直至桑榆暮景  我已失去太多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.15,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Something is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.81,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}A story is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:32.44,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Do you like it?  Do you hate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:35.11,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Got any doubts? I don't think so. Let's jump into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.61,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}C-C-Come and kick up! Are you ready ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:40.44,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}C-C-Come and kick up! Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:43.16,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}C-C-Come and kick up! Are you ready ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.75,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}C-C-Come and kick up! Now let'sgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:49.79,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Bounce, 高鳴る鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.50,OP - JP,,1000,0,0,,{\blur4}No doubts, 感じる波動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.63,OP - JP,,1000,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}研ぎ澄ます感性をCONTROL
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.70,OP - JP,,800,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Like a 歌舞伎的 Playing a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:57.94,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}When you're in trouble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.97,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What's a Hero? Break the old ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:02.51,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What's a Hero? Make new waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:05.18,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's a hero! Save all the days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:08.39,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You can be who you are & be free yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.58,OP - JP,,600,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}Is this where it ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.85,OP - JP,,600,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}No no 終わらない Broken road
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:13.48,OP - JP,,600,0,0,,{\blur4}続くStory
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.32,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}信じるのは　自分のHEART
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.13,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大義より仁義　異論はなし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.28,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}BELIEVE IN YOURSELF
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:22.17,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}背負った誓い　歪ませない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:24.54,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}巻き起こせ　革命REVOLUTION
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.62,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}挑め世界　沈ませない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.32,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}舞い上がる　異端NO IMITATION
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.97,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}YOU AND I FEEL ALIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:36.34,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}Overdrive It's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:39.18,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}誰がヒーロー？ Break the old ways
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:41.68,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}お前がヒーロー！ MAKE NEW WAVES
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:44.31,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}C-C-Come and kick up! Are you ready ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.06,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}C-C-Come and kick up! Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.88,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}C-C-Come and kick up! Are you ready ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.94,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,200)}C-C-Come and kick up! NOW LET'S GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.15,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是什么悄然而至
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.81,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}传奇即将拉开序幕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:32.44,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你会喜不自胜还是鄙夷不屑？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:35.11,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}亦或者犹豫不决？ 而我心意已决  共赴这传奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.61,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:40.44,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！即刻出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:43.16,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.75,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！即刻出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:49.79,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}心潮澎湃  热血沸腾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.50,OP - CN,,0,1000,0,,{\blur4}毋庸置疑  感受波动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.63,OP - CN,,0,1000,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}控制好敏锐的感性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.70,OP - CN,,0,800,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}像歌舞伎那般演绎自我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:57.94,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}当你深陷泥潭  是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.97,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}何为英雄？ 革旧鼎新
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:02.51,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}何为英雄？ 独领风骚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:05.18,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是英雄！ 救民济世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:08.39,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你大可率性而为  逍遥自在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.58,OP - CN,,600,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}可这就是英雄的终点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.85,OP - CN,,600,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}不  艰难险阻永无止尽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:13.48,OP - CN,,600,0,0,,{\blur4}传奇还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.32,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}坚守本心  矢志不移
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.13,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}仁义高于大义  无可辩驳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.28,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:22.17,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}一言九鼎  驷马难追
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:24.54,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}揭竿而起  掀起革命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.62,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}挑战世界  宁死不屈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.32,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}展翅高飞  去做那绝无仅有的异端
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.97,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}感受彼此生命的共振
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:36.34,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}放手一搏  全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:39.18,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}何为英雄？ 革旧鼎新
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:41.68,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你是英雄！ 独领风骚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:44.31,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.06,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！即刻出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.88,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.94,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,200)}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！即刻出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:35.89,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}孤独な　影が伸びて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:42.13,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}夕日が今日も　乾いた大地に消える
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:47.99,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}さすらう　渡り鳥は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:55.49,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}すり切れた　羽を引き継ぎ　歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:22:00.03,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}滑稽に　みえ見えるかい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:05.65,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}泥にまみれても　這い上がるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:09.05,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}Becuase we're loose stars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:12.10,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}最後の時まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:15.50,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Catch the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:18.49,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}止めない　翼広げ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.49,0:22:24.12,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}戦う者たちに　レクイエムはいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.66,0:22:26.23,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Sky high
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:30.69,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}想いは遥か高く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.69,0:22:38.66,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雲を切り裂いて　あの空の彼方へと
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.02,0:21:35.89,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}孤独的身影被余晖拉长
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.89,0:21:42.13,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}今日 夕阳照旧沉落在干涸的大地尽头
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.13,0:21:47.99,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那只漂泊的候鸟
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.99,0:21:55.49,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}拖着伤痕累累的羽翼 缓步前进
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.34,0:22:00.03,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}他人眼里 这很可笑吧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.03,0:22:05.65,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}即便满身泥泞 也要奋勇斗争
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.87,0:22:09.05,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}只因为我们是桀骜的星辰
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.05,0:22:12.10,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}直至最后一刻
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.82,0:22:15.50,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}乘风破浪
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.50,0:22:18.49,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}势不可挡 展翅高飞
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.49,0:22:24.12,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}英勇的战士无需安魂曲
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.66,0:22:26.23,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}天高任鸟飞
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.50,0:22:30.69,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}思念飞向遥远的彼方
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.69,0:22:38.66,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}冲云破雾 直至世界尽头
